HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
4-5-0-8, Wild: 8
(four, five, zero, eight; Wild: eight)
